      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "entry, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "because then there were no gates. The meaning is, that all things were now restored to their primitive order; and the several persons took those offices upon them, which their ancestors had before them.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
